 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18e18a8330640ba4e6120b8668445c59cd08916b","tid":334073,"uid":42524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T12:43:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"31fe74603fc0f6ea5487ad9b3c24dd1df5b99e58","tid":334073,"uid":43124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:19:42.000Z","msg":"雖然唔熟cs 但加油呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />努力追夢 翻工最重要自己鍾意"},{"pid":"9701ddf2450226b2521e6ffd2172f550b7db4be7","tid":334073,"uid":58778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:43:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>p仔無出頭<br />\n你讀同唔讀入職都係邊做邊學<br />\n叫做有個底 上手快少少<br />\n學既係it狗思維，<br />\n樣樣都係要自學同google<br />\n<br />\n前景咪it狗&hellip;<br />\n做到30 40 50歲，<br />\n人工都係每年施舍多你幾百<br />\n<br />\n好悲哀 雖然好似行行都係咁<br />\n工字無出頭。<br />\n<br />\n利申 前p仔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽巴打講好似真係冇咩前景咁 我都聽過做IT冇乜保障 唔似其他工咁做得耐有經驗 轉一轉工就多幾千咁 但我覺得自己幾鍾意program 應該會做得比而家呢份工更加有熱誠 所以想睇下有冇方法轉行<br />\n不過好多謝你覆得咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw巴打介唔介意講下而家轉咗做邊行？嗰行仲關唔關program事咖？"},{"pid":"1795e4fed386a705375e84c90578eca3c4ead21f","tid":334073,"uid":51747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:46:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>本身major咩先</blockquote><br />\nLogistics呀 物流 但自己本身對programming好有興趣 係入錯科就浪費咗4年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />巴打有冇咩意見呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好有興趣既可以接下freelance甚至空餘寫下app<br />\n<br />\n好多人中學時以為自己好有興趣入去讀CS苦不堪言<br />\n然後好多人讀實戰型沙紙以為自己好有興趣出至黎做code狗話咁快就磨滅晒"},{"pid":"2d2fff7ce45b1e6d01281e4e70273e985101e6b9","tid":334073,"uid":58778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T16:12:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>本身major咩先</blockquote><br />\nLogistics呀 物流 但自己本身對programming好有興趣 係入錯科就浪費咗4年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />巴打有冇咩意見呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好有興趣既可以接下freelance甚至空餘寫下app<br />\n<br />\n好多人中學時以為自己好有興趣入去讀CS苦不堪言<br />\n然後好多人讀實戰型沙紙以為自己好有興趣出至黎做code狗話咁快就磨滅晒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都係嘅 當日日都對住d code就未必再鍾意打code<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bbe77dfb927dba8abbbc769eaf1efabc87db8da","tid":334073,"uid":51747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T16:25:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>本身major咩先</blockquote><br />\nLogistics呀 物流 但自己本身對programming好有興趣 係入錯科就浪費咗4年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />巴打有冇咩意見呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好有興趣既可以接下freelance甚至空餘寫下app<br />\n<br />\n好多人中學時以為自己好有興趣入去讀CS苦不堪言<br />\n然後好多人讀實戰型沙紙以為自己好有興趣出至黎做code狗話咁快就磨滅晒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都係嘅 當日日都對住d code就未必再鍾意打code<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而事實上你喺香港做code狗都唔一定有得比你日日對你想對既code<br />\n<br />\n例如三分一寫doc填form，三分一對住西客，三分一寫code不過只係執人啲屎無得比你發揮<br />\n<br />\n轉工囉，點知轉完就對住西上司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無錯行行都可以係咁，但做其他行業你仲會有寫code既興趣同熱誠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7b94bc2ef89fc94fcc08265995896227e69828a","tid":334073,"uid":51472,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T16:28:13.000Z","msg":"加油呀巴打<br />\n我都做完酒店轉左it狗<br />\n雖然由頭開始過 人工又低<br />\n但我起碼開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ec75e9aaa8ffd6a0cd88405d6e0a582165f6bcd","tid":334073,"uid":51472,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T16:30:44.000Z","msg":"巴打唔介意可以喺systematic 間野考張programming language 嘅cert<br />\n<br />\n因為就算自學到識飛都冇人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cbdcba455ccb6f3c2a00