img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因爲master好似係俾有it degree底嘅人讀多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我本身修cs major，驚入去讀唔上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以會諗其他進修途徑多啲 巴打都係it master？"},{"pid":"e283ba730e796292453822e6a95b124d26887b68","tid":334073,"uid":58778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:46:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打唔介意可以喺systematic 間野考張programming language 嘅cert<br />\n<br />\n因為就算自學到識飛都冇人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\ncert 唔太重要.. skill 呢啲落場見真章</blockquote><br />\n我當然明啦 但冇cert一定比有cert更蝕底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能hr scan人嘅時候已經俾人西走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因爲之前已經apply過好多，但全部都冇回音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />anyway多謝巴打鼓勵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f6e74a71e8a6b5039875dbe07d8502a28289d3e","tid":334073,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:47:23.000Z","msg":"30歲你一定後悔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84d2b9a5739b8518dd7c1f7245d4dbee3b321923","tid":334073,"uid":78630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:40:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>喺連登做IT 唔會有人阻止你架</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實係咪好小人長做？</blockquote><br />\n點會少人長做...</blockquote><br />\nsorry呀因為其實都唔係好清楚 以為it流失率都幾高 上面班巴打又講到好灰咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有心做既話其實唔難搵工.. 公司炒唔炒人就睇大環境.."},{"pid":"c30c75eafadcec04680a3814d1ca49a43ecfd116","tid":334073,"uid":78630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:41:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>30歲你一定後悔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我做IT, 今年就30.. 暫時都未話後悔既"},{"pid":"407d30f1334742e985f34f9b6fae2f81d9b965de","tid":334073,"uid":78630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:42:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋呢幾日諗諗下仲有多小小問題 有冇巴打可以解答多小小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 想知而家it公司入面多唔多人唔係major修cs, 但公司俾佢邊做邊學同進修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因爲咁樣可以慳翻啲時間 人工低啲都冇所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 上面有巴打提過ou有得讀，其實我自己都search過，知道poly之前好似都有得讀pt degree，想問下有冇巴打係過來人？同埋邊間讀會好啲？</blockquote><br />\n1. 我諗唔多.. 除非間公司好重視tech.."},{"pid":"1ffd076505d621289772bca750f05181738add79","tid":334073,"uid":105553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T16:42:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>CS related (EE, Maths, 甚至 Physics）會容易D。無有關學位或文憑難D過到HR。</blockquote><br />\n我都明啊！所以就想上嚟問下有冇好嘅路數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋巴打係咪都係讀cs咖？介唔介意講多小小？</blockquote><br />\n如果job ad係話請CS related degrees，甘EE同maths有修過幾科programming嘅都不妨試試send個CV去申請。如果係再遠d例如physics就都可以試試不過機會俾EE同maths低D。<br />\n<br />\n如果有錢有時間可以讀返個CS MSc。不過至少一年還要俾一大筆。<br />\n<br />\n就算俾你有機會interview都要過到先得，你自修都要追返人地兩三年讀嘅野。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，我係讀CS同engine畢業，多個一個degree，engine都係讀電腦。"},{"pid":"e1a8601126e294205dbd1e731b99e75aa4f9108a","tid":334073,"uid":105553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T16:45:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解唔自學再上master？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因爲master好似係俾有it degree底嘅人讀多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我本身修cs major，驚入去讀唔上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以會諗其他進修途徑多啲 巴打都係it master？</blockquote><br />\n咩major？你數學底係點？linear algebra（matrix，vector eigen value，etc）讀過未？"},{"pid":"0f20471d0974b5eab22dcb13204bc6c97e1bb880","tid":334073,"uid":58778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T23:56:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>30歲你一定後悔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打點解會咁講呢？有冇嘢可以分享下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5386ab95dc376069c9f771e98bad7dcc4f9ae39a","tid":334073,"uid":58778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T23:59:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>30歲你一定後悔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我做IT, 今年就30.. 暫時都未話後悔既</blockquote><br />\n係呢行做咗幾耐？想知IT除咗打code之外會唔會有其他duty？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab6eba703ba9342147a62edf77b2fe0580a46e0f","tid":334073,"uid":126897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T00:02:45.000Z","msg":"portfolio"},{"pid":"3db7a141ad32c928b67e5d0a1e60a568f82a47bb","tid":334073,"uid":51747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T00:21:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>30歲你一定後悔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我做IT, 今年就30.. 暫時都未話後悔既</blockquote><br />\n係呢行做咗幾耐？想知IT除咗打code之外會唔會有其他duty？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做左十年，香港做programmer點會淨係打code，成個SDLC都係你做晒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算大公司都可能只係唔比你掂production，餘下九成都係你"},{"pid":"d720831dd2a2fd107acc3891712790dacc4cac53","tid":334073,"uid":58778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T00:25:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>CS related (EE, Maths, 甚至 Physics）會容易D。無有關學位或文憑難D過到HR。</blockquote><br />\n我都明啊！所以就想上嚟問下有冇好嘅路數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋巴打係咪都係讀cs咖？介唔介意講多小小？</blockquote><br />\n如果job ad係話請CS related degrees，甘EE同maths有修過幾科programming嘅都不妨試試send個CV去申請。如果係再遠d例如physics就都可以試試不過機會俾EE同maths低D。<br />\n<br />\n如果有錢有時間可以讀返個CS MSc。不過至少一年還要俾一大筆。<br />\n<br />\n就算俾你有機會interview都要過到先得，你自修都要追返人地兩三年讀嘅野。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，我係讀CS同engine畢業，多個一個degree，engine都係讀電腦。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n感謝巴打回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我有考慮過讀個cs master 不過佢嗰啲課程似係俾從事緊cs嗰d人讀 而唔似係俾想做cs呢行嘅人讀 所以就唔知自己應唔應該讀個CS MSc<br />\n除咗master呢條路 我諗緊可唔可以讀多個degree 見到巴打有多個degree 想問多幾個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 你讀兩個degree大概要幾耐時間到？<br />\n2. 如果我想讀多個degree係咪要係jupas再報過？而家想讀嘅話係咪要等下年？<br />\n3. 第二個degree同第一個degree嘅課程會唔會重疊咗？<br />\n唔該哂巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5e4afb9a3aeb9a96b5dc6b342a2f3bccba7a2c4","tid":334073,"uid":78630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T00:31:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>CS related (EE, Maths, 甚至 Physics）會容易D。無有關學位或文憑難D過到HR。</blockquote><br />\n我都明啊！所以就想上嚟問下有冇好嘅路數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋巴打係咪都係讀cs咖？介唔介意講多小小？</blockquote><br />\n如果job ad係話請CS related degrees，甘EE同maths有修過幾科programming嘅都不妨試試send個CV去申請。如果係再遠d例如physics就都可以試試不過機會俾EE同maths低D。<br />\n<br />\n如果有錢有時間可以讀返個CS MSc。不過至少一年還要俾一大筆。<br />\n<br />\n就算俾你有機會interview都要過到先得，你自修都要追返人地兩三年讀嘅野。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，我係讀CS同engine畢業，多個一個degree，engine都係讀電腦。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n感謝巴打回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我有考慮過讀個cs master 不過佢嗰啲課程似係俾從事緊cs嗰d人讀 而唔似係俾想做cs呢行嘅人讀 所以就唔知自己應唔應該讀個CS MSc<br />\n除咗master呢條路 我諗緊可唔可以讀多個degree 見到巴打有多個degree 想問多幾個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 你讀兩個degree大概要幾耐時間到？<br />\n2. 如果我想讀多個degree係咪要係jupas再報過？而家想讀嘅話係咪要等下年？<br />\n3. 第二個degree同第一個degree嘅課程會唔會重疊咗？<br />\n唔該哂巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你呢個case 讀master 就ok, 你又唔係去做research, 我覺得唔需要為左做呢行而讀個degree"},{"pid":"c12a04f0837d6b574975eff602492befb6941f31","tid":334073,"uid":58778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T00:33:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解唔自學再上master？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因爲master好似係俾有it degree底嘅人讀多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我本身修cs major，驚入去讀唔上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以會諗其他進修途徑多啲 巴打都係it master？</blockquote><br />\n咩major？你數學底係點？linear algebra（matrix，vector eigen value，etc）讀過未？</blockquote><br />\n我修物流 係engine school入面嘅 係大學都有讀過linear algebra, matrix vector呢啲我都冇問題 本身係大學都有讀過下programming嘅課程，有vba Python Java 甚至係apps 不過我學嘅都係好basic 自問比唔上讀咗4年cs嘅人 所以就唔知master啱唔啱我呢啲想補底嘅人讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}